        {
            "title": "Stephen Jen：若伊朗衝突加劇 應做空美元兌日圓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 總部位於倫敦的資產管理公司Eurizon SLJ Capital執行長Stephen Jen表示，如果中東衝突加劇，投資者應做空美元兌日圓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在全球資產遭拋售之際，日圓可能吸引避險資金流入，促使日本國內投資者將資金匯回本土。這可能逆轉當前趨勢：當前日圓持續走弱，由於日本是能源淨進口國，伊朗戰爭引發的油價飆升加劇通膨擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為做空美元兌日圓是我最看好的交易，因為我覺得頂部已近，」他在接受採訪時表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-de81d91c-ae04-377b-ad20-a4e3081c1908-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自2月28日戰爭爆發以來，日圓兌美元已下跌2.6%。周五，日圓跌破1美元兌160日圓這一關鍵水平。交易員一直密切關注這一關口，因為日本金融當局2024年曾於該水平附近出手干預以支撐日圓。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aqtU7gi8XLCiy8VefkOXzg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0b2b7f13f2525bb9a5925a52502ad2af\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jen表示，若衝突加劇，美元兌大多數貨幣將走強，但日本的情況可能不同。他指出，日本投資者持有的海外資產規模約相當於該國國內生產毛額的90%，若戰爭引發全球拋售，將促使這些投資者投資國內，從而提振日圓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jen以其「美元微笑」理論聞名，該理論認為，當美國經濟處於強勁成長或深度衰退時，美元均會走強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Stephen Jen Says Short Dollar Versus Yen If Iran War Intensifies</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 George Lei.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/stephen-jen-%E8%8B%A5%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87-%E6%87%89%E5%81%9A%E7%A9%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%85%8C%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93-230732529.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-28 23:36:52",
